                    text: "The ED offers dependable performance and good durability, but early models (1987–1989) had reliability concerns, particularly camshaft and lifter wear. Later revisions (post-1990) improved component durability, so well-maintained examples can exceed 150,000 km. Regular servicing with OEM-specified oil (10W-30) and timely lifter maintenance greatly enhance longevity.",
