                    text: "The most frequent issues are camshaft and lifter wear, intake manifold gasket leaks, and water pump coolant leaks. These are well-documented in Daihatsu service bulletins. Lifter issues are linked to oil pressure and lubrication, while gasket problems stem from material aging under heat. Coolant leaks are design-related and affect pre-1990 units most.",
